title: StarTalk Live! from SF Sketchfest 2016 (Part 1)
description: We’re going to Mars! Join commander Bill Nye and executive officer Eugene Mirman as we explore the Red Planet with NASA Planetary Science Division Director Jim Green, “The Martian” author Andy Weir, and Maeve Higgins. RECORDED LIVE, ADULT LANGUAGE.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
